legendaryGobblerPrice().details: The price of a legendary gobbler decays as gobblers are minted. The first legendary auction begins when 1 LEGENDARY_AUCTION_INTERVAL worth of gobblers are minted, and the price decays linearly while the next interval of gobblers are minted. Every time an additional interval is minted, a new auction begins until all legendaries have been sold.

returns._0: price of legendary gobbler, in terms of gobblers.
